---
const painPoints = [
  {
    title: "Patients book on WhatsApp",
    body: "Then forget. Or you forget. No system. No reminder. No show."
  },
  {
    title: "Paper intake forms",
    body: "Lost, misread, or 20 minutes of staff time to process. Every single patient."
  },
  {
    title: "Follow-ups done manually",
    body: "When staff remember. Which isn't always. Most patients never hear from you again after their first visit."
  },
  {
    title: "No data. No insight.",
    body: "You cannot see which services are growing, which are failing, or why patients leave."
  }
];
---

<section class="bg-[#F7F9FC] py-[48px] md:py-[80px] px-5 md:px-0">
  <div class="max-w-container mx-auto">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue mb-4 font-body">Does This Sound Familiar?</div>
      <h2 class="text-[26px] md:text-[38px] font-bold text-navy mb-6 font-display leading-[1.2]">
        Right now, your clinic probably<br class="hidden md:block" /> 
        looks something like this.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[16px] text-muted max-w-[560px] mb-12 font-body leading-[1.65]">
        These are not small frustrations. They compound daily — 
        costing you patients, revenue, and staff morale.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6">
      {painPoints.map((point, index) => (
        <div class={`reveal reveal-delay-${(index % 3) + 1} bg-white border-l-[3px] border-red-soft rounded-r-[12px] shadow-sm p-4 md:p-5 flex flex-col justify-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200`}>
          <h3 class="text-[13px] font-medium text-navy mb-1.5 font-body">{point.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-muted leading-[1.6] font-body">{point.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
